its exactly the same thing. ek movie do movie teen movie. superstars ke ladke ghar par baithe hain. the first step will always be made easy and should be. to maintin it isnt an easy task. bollywood is also a business industry. its not a talent platform to be precise.

apke papa ke business ke saath fame milta to wo line me lagte. they do join your dad as employees but they will never be the owners unless they start their own business. similarly you can be a part of the business in bollywood but not inherit it till you have your family in it.
agar aap bollywood ki shuruwaat pe jaenge to wo virasat hi hai. industry viraasat hi hoti hai my sister. stage viraasat nahi hota. faraq hai.

u said "tum ameeron ki", u started it. bhai kyon na kare wo maje. unke gharwalon ne mehnat ki hai unkle liye. shahrukh khan ne zameen se mehnat ki jab sanjay dutt, salman etc wagehra industry se they to aj bachche maje le rahe hain. tum aaj karo to kal tumhare bachche maje lenge.

bollywood is business. its not a platform to showcase talent. it is a business where u sell your self as a product to entertain the masses and get fame and money in return. art dikhani hai to theatre karo. stage karo.  talent ki ladai nahi fame ki ladai hai.
